results: Your parents don't miss you and just feel obligated to talk to you! You are their greatest disappointment, and you will never live up to the high expectations set by your older sibling. You will forever live in their shadow, and your parents will leave everything to your high-achieving sibling and will only leave you one bean.
Your parents don't miss you, and you are in fact a horrible person. Your parents are right to disown you. I am sorry, but you will need to put yourself up for adoption right now.
